WEBVTT

01:40.740 --> 01:45.930
[SPEED AND LOVE]

01:46.190 --> 01:48.810
[Episode 19]

01:53.130 --> 01:55.789
Bantu aku lihat, lebih bagus
memakai yang mana?

02:00.970 --> 02:02.970
